title: TORREY MEISTER - CHAPTER 1 "WELCOME TO TEAM O'NEILL!"
description: In November of 2013 Torrey won the Coldwater Classic Invitational and took home the "winner take all" grand prize, which was a sponsorship from O'Neill consisting of $50,000 to travel the world and compete in the World Qualifying Series in pursuit of making the World Championship Tour.
